    "Future work comparing model performance in relation to prompt length would provide valuable insight into this tradeoff.",
    "The cost of manual annotation varies by location, but in the United States can be estimated to be the minimum wage per hour for that state.",
    "As of January 2024 in the state of Washington, the minimum wage was $16.28/hr 42.",
    "To analyze 25,217 notes would have cost approximately $9,442, substantially higher than either LLM.",
    "An analysis of the time and cost per note between LLMs and manual annotation can be found in Fig. 6."
